B^c\cap C^c=\bigcup_{n=2}^sE_n
n\in\{2,\dots,s\}
E_n=\{x\in X:x_n=H\text{ and }x_k=T\text{ for }k=1,\dots,n-1\}\;;
\varphi_n:E_n\to E_1:x\mapsto\langle x_{k+n-1}:k\in\Bbb Z^+\rangle\;,
